headline: 1-800-Flowers.com (FLWS) Reports Q1 Loss, Lags Revenue Estimates
summary: 1-800-Flowers.com (FLWS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -40.68% and -1.45%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
